title: 이달의소녀탐구 #462 (LOONA TV #462)
summary:
0:01 -- HaSeul asks how does everyone feel about the entire group being together.
0:11 -- They start telling their stories. YeoJin starts off by telling the story of the massage she got from HaSeul (Joint Stretches). The rest pursuade her to do it despite HaSeul saying no.
0:24 -- YeoJin commences to punch HaSeul. (She does not care).
0:29 -- Choerry, YeoJin, Chuu, Olivia Hye perform Rosy. Go Won joins them. HeeJin covers her rap part.
